normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同朋友各叫一件cake<br />\n其實唔太好食 只係第一次去想試下<br />\n我建議你可以嗌一件已經夠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yagQcCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyagQcCH.jpg&h=00af258c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9147df5fd7305ea868fb9b6d19551ca99ff9cee5","tid":108012,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n汗蒸幕 推介去龍山站果間</blockquote><br />\n但係我果晚落機之後好似首爾站落腳最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首爾站果間唔錯，去過兩次</blockquote><br />\n想問入面有無野食架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有十幾種野食，價錢唔貴<br />\n有一層比人訓覺添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fa56bd4693d3c6c4c9369683529a9338805a5b","tid":108012,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭uo去 22:45到首爾<br />\n<br />\nDay1<br />\n諗住搭00:15凌晨巴士去首爾站 <br />\n係汗蒸幕Silloam Sauna 訓一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay2<br />\n1100 check in 住弘大<br />\n1.建大貨櫃 <br />\n2.明洞<br />\n3.弘大<br />\n4.首爾站 樂天超市<br />\n<br />\n呢日會唔會太chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知巴打你出左發未<br />\nSilloam sauna係好野黎 <br />\n記得係機場線3號出口 唔係首爾站3號 <br />\n完全兩邊黎<br />\n去完汗蒸幕 朝頭早出黎 格黎就係首爾超市<br />\n超市行李免費keep3個鐘 <br />\n<br />\n去之前睇好左個地鐵地圖先<br />\n你day 2跟個呢個順序會玩自己<br />\n明洞同首爾差兩個地鐵站 唔洗轉<br />\n首爾同弘大差兩個西鐵站 唔洗轉<br />\n雖然都係搭車 不過你鍾意啦"},{"pid":"bbd8e43093da3f3a3db3f99940bf12c6f0077ad1","tid":108012,"uid":13321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭uo去 22:45到首爾<br />\n<br />\nDay1<br />\n諗住搭00:15凌晨巴士去首爾站 <br />\n係汗蒸幕Silloam Sauna 訓一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay2<br />\n1100 check in 住弘大<br />\n1.建大貨櫃 <br />\n2.明洞<br />\n3.弘大<br />\n4.首爾站 樂天超市<br />\n<br />\n呢日會唔會太chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知巴打你出左發未<br />\nSilloam sauna係好野黎 <br />\n記得係機場線3號出口 唔係首爾站3號 <br />\n完全兩邊黎<br />\n去完汗蒸幕 朝頭早出黎 格黎就係首爾超市<br />\n超市行李免費keep3個鐘 <br />\n<br />\n去之前睇好左個地鐵地圖先<br />\n你day 2跟個呢個順序會玩自己<br />\n明洞同首爾差兩個地鐵站 唔洗轉<br />\n首爾同弘大差兩個西鐵站 唔洗轉<br />\n雖然都係搭車 不過你鍾意啦</blockquote><br />\n我三月頭去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好大幫助 唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507799ddea25ccac3dc2e69c21edae8e78620282","tid":108012,"uid":49366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上星期先去完 行程同你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨櫃真心 冇野行     只係去影下假相同食個彩虹蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個蛋糕好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n麻麻地 兩個人食都好頂胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beac65cad373a19c0d6af693baa631c17f841d4d","tid":108012,"uid":54492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"首爾塔<br />\n樂天世界必去"},{"pid":"b5bd95d2a3cd1974617352310f65177a40ed96e9","tid":108012,"uid":41755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"走果日凌晨機。打算係汗蒸幕hea陣，暫定住siloam/機場果間spa on air。無知一問呢兩間係咪都係直接walk in就得，定可能會好多人，要打定去預約。唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cla