<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ef78c91dc8c1634258bbc4582aa685088e8f7c","tid":108012,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>首爾塔<br />\n樂天世界必去</blockquote><br />\n唔好上觀景台<br />\n冇野好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n觀景台唔洗上去</blockquote><br />\n樂天世界唔買fast pass唔好去<br />\n同埋岩小朋友多啲<br />\n係去everland好啲"},{"pid":"f35440eb83b1f03100349a74567f6919914222d6","tid":108012,"uid":41755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>走果日凌晨機。打算係汗蒸幕hea陣，暫定住siloam/機場果間spa on air。無知一問呢兩間係咪都係直接walk in就得，定可能會好多人，要打定去預約。唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsiloam walk-in就得</blockquote><br />\n唔該曬巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd4d24b86d63d6b8090c36e78da7295f5724b08","tid":108012,"uid":1239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"Day1唔好咁排<br />\n你住弘大 又走去建大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要去明洞兌錢的話 兌完可以去下東大門廣藏市場<br />\n食下傳統嘢 又可以食一隻雞<br />\n再有時間可以去光化門行景福宮<br />\n唔知你鍾唔鍾意歷史嘢啦<br />\n光化門世宗大王個銅像隔離有歷史博物館<br />\n主打韓國近代史 都值得睇下<br />\n鍾意文具精品 可以去光化門 教保文庫<br />\n或者東大門玩具文具街<br />\n<br />\n再有時間先翻弘大行<br />\n<br />\n如果你day4要去梨大(同行有女仔的話 冇就skip)就連住新村弘大<br />\n新村食燒肉首選 再唔係鍾意食海鮮的話 去任燒海鮮鋪都幾正下<br />\n總之新村食嘢為主<br />\n咪鬼去姜虎東個間又貴又唔好食<br />\n弘大就食嘢行街都有 但你最好五六點之後先去 晏就冇乜鋪開<br />\n不過想買衫又平 其實應該去江南高速公路站 個度地下街可以行一日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申韓國住"},{"pid":"84d88c58ed8145f477ed3fb1511767d1da8513c1","tid":108012,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"下個月尾都會去韓國<br />\n搭uo 2130機 韓國1:30落機 <br />\n但酒店2點先checkin <br />\n12個鐘可以點過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250b43c94f1068076ec0db8cb58939f35e2f3479","tid":108012,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下個月尾都會去韓國<br />\n搭uo 2130機 韓國1:30落機 <br />\n但酒店2點先checkin <br />\n12個鐘可以點過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n補充 住東大門酒店"},{"pid":"8d645604dca88a7090bdc53c010d5ba1fb94ec36","tid":108012,"uid":1239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"補充下 如果你鍾意飲酒落club先好去建大<br />\n建大都係飲酒食飯居多<br />\n<br />\n同埋你行完弘大新村梨大就可以去首爾站lotte 坐的士好快到<br />\n<br />\n韓國坐的士 除非你好有錢 好注重安全駕駛啦<br />\n唔係都唔好坐黑的 黑的收費有5000won起<br />\n橙的銀的就3000won"},{"pid":"ec0d54fd3cb60c933f2a8301eafa6f9cf572b182","tid":108012,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"下個月第四次單拖去首爾留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d6025c0d856130932c18dfab8dcd15c6e27e8c","tid":108012,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補充下 如果你鍾意飲酒落club先好去建大<br />\n建大都係飲酒食飯居多<br />\n<br />\n同埋你行完弘大新村梨大就可以去首爾站lotte 坐的士好快到<br />\n<br />\n韓國坐的士 除非你好有錢 好注重安全駕駛啦<br />\n唔係都唔好坐黑的 黑的收費有5000won起<br />\n橙的銀的就3000won</blockquote><br />\n想問下韓國的士司機聽唔聽得明普通話或者英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係要比個韓國地址佢"},{"pid":"76d2e2b173d13deec01df8e520b65a583ec506cb","tid":108012,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"